---
source: crates/kul-wasm/tests/format.rs
expression: formatted
---
# A polygamous household.
#
# Kul records concurrent marriages directly: a person with two or more
# un-ended marriages is a *hub*. Khalid is married to Aisha, Layla, and
# Mariam at the same time. Each marriage is its own `marriage` statement;
# nothing else is special about the syntax.
#
# One rule governs the shape (and it is enforced — rule R14): the hub
# must be the host (first-listed spouse) of every one of their concurrent
# marriages. That keeps the picture unambiguous — Khalid is the single
# anchor the household fans out from. If a marriage listed the spouse
# first, the validator would flag it and the fix is to swap the two
# names.
#
# The renderer draws the hub once. Each spouse fans out to their own
# side, and each marriage's children gather under that marriage's edge —
# so half-siblings stay in distinct groups, one group per marriage. Here
# the whole fan also sits inside Khalid's own birth family, one
# generation below his parents.

# ---- Khalid's birth family ----
person omar    name:"Omar Al-Rashid"    gender:male    born:~1925
person fatima  name:"Fatima Al-Rashid"  gender:female  born:1928-04-02

marriage m_omar_fatima omar fatima  start:1945-08-17

person khalid  name:"Khalid Al-Rashid"  gender:male  born:1950-03-29
  birth m_omar_fatima

# ---- Khalid's three concurrent marriages (he hosts each) ----
person aisha   name:"Aisha Al-Rashid"   gender:female  born:1955-07-11
person layla   name:"Layla Al-Rashid"   gender:female  born:1958-02-23
person mariam  name:"Mariam Al-Rashid"  gender:female  born:1962-10-19

marriage m_khalid_aisha  khalid aisha   start:1975-05-04
marriage m_khalid_layla  khalid layla   start:1980-09-16
marriage m_khalid_mariam khalid mariam  start:1985-12-28

# ---- Children, grouped by marriage ----
person yusuf  name:"Yusuf Al-Rashid"  gender:male  born:1977-06-13
  birth m_khalid_aisha

person zahra  name:"Zahra Al-Rashid"  gender:female  born:1982-01-08
  birth m_khalid_layla

person hassan  name:"Hassan Al-Rashid"  gender:male    born:1987-03-21
  birth m_khalid_mariam
person noor    name:"Noor Al-Rashid"    gender:female  born:1990-11-07
  birth m_khalid_mariam
